'''Bonestar Pirates''' were a group of [[Corellian/Legends|Corellian]] rogues, once led by [[Loka Hask]]. During this time, they were pursued by the [[Corellian Security Force]]s for several crimes. An interstellar chase resulted in the pirates landing on [[Gus Treta Inner-System Market Station]] to create a diversion. The diversion involved the destruction of a fuel depot, owned by the [[Antilles family/Legends|Antilles family]]. The devastation, caused when the pirates lifted off while still coupled to the fuel dispensers, destroyed the Antilles' depot and killed [[Jagged Antilles|Jagged]] and [[Zena Antilles]]. [[Wedge Antilles/Legends|Wedge Antilles]] was safely off the station when the "accident" occurred. He and [[Booster Terrik]] pursued the pirates, destroying their ship and leaving them for dead.

